Subject Re Shaft drives and Wheelies From Stafford John Stafford In article John Daker wrote In a previous article says Mike Terry asks Is it possible to do a wheelie on a motorcycle with shaft drive No It is imposible due to the shaft The centripital effects of the rotating shaft counteract any tendency for the front wheel to lift off the This is true as evinced by the popularity of shaft drive drag John Stafford Minnesota State University Winona All standard disclaimers